BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[FFXIV] Jollibee x FINAL FANTASY XIV Collaboration Campaign - Get 
 the Eat Chicken Emote!
DTSTART:20260417T141000Z
DTEND:20260501T141000Z
DTSTAMP:20260423T080141Z
UID:2bb1740a2baf@mmo-calendar
DESCRIPTION:FINAL FANTASY XIV and Jollibee join forces to fuel Warriors of
  Light starting Tuesday\, April 21\, 2026! For a limited time\, purchase c
 ollaboration meals or merchandise to earn your own Eat Chicken emote!\n\nF
 urthermore\, in celebration of Fan Festival 2026 in Anaheim\, Jollibee's A
 naheim store will be decked out in FFXIV-themed decor from April 21 to May
  31! Jollibee x FINAL FANTASY XIV stickers will be available for customers
  at the Anaheim store while supplies last.\n\nRead on for details.
URL:https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/topics/detail/2ca9077926ee36f
 137c7969e60447b75dcaadf17
END:VEVENT
